5:["$","$L11",null,{"dictionary":{"nav":{"home":"Home","services":"Services","about":"About","contact":"Contact","getStarted":"Get Started"},"hero":{"badge":"Malaysia's Leading IT Solutions Provider","title1":"Building Digital","title2":"Excellence","description":"We craft innovative CRM systems, project management platforms, and cloud solutions that transform businesses and drive growth.","exploreServices":"Explore Services","contactUs":"Contact Us","projectsValue":"50+","projectsLabel":"Projects","clientsValue":"20+","clientsLabel":"Clients","yearsValue":"4+","yearsLabel":"Years"},"stats":{"items":[{"value":"40+","label":"Global Partners"},{"value":"2K+","label":"Users Trained"},{"value":"100%","label":"Client Satisfaction"},{"value":"40K","label":"Professional Learners"}]},"services":{"badge":"OUR SERVICES","title":"What We","titleHighlight":"Offer","description":"Comprehensive IT solutions designed to elevate your business to the next level.","learnMore":"Learn More","items":[{"title":"Custom CRM Systems","description":"Tailored customer relationship management solutions that streamline your sales pipeline and boost customer engagement.","features":["Sales Automation","Lead Tracking","Custom Reports","API Integration"]},{"title":"Project Management","description":"Powerful platforms to plan, track, and deliver projects efficiently with real-time collaboration tools.","features":["Task Management","Team Collaboration","Progress Tracking","Resource Planning"]},{"title":"Cloud & Business Email","description":"Enterprise-grade AWS cloud infrastructure and professional email solutions for seamless operations.","features":["AWS Setup","Email Hosting","Security","24/7 Support"]},{"title":"Training & Consulting","description":"Expert-led training programs and strategic consulting to empower your team with cutting-edge skills.","features":["Corporate Training","Workshops","1-on-1 Coaching","Certification"]}]},"about":{"badge":"WHY CHOOSE US","title":"Built for","titleHighlight":"Success","description":"We combine technical expertise with business insight to deliver solutions that matter.","features":[{"title":"Innovation First","description":"Cutting-edge solutions tailored to your business needs."},{"title":"Enterprise Security","description":"Bank-grade security protocols protecting your data."},{"title":"Fast Delivery","description":"Agile methodology ensuring rapid deployment."},{"title":"Scalable Growth","description":"Solutions that grow with your business."}]},"testimonials":{"badge":"TESTIMONIALS","title":"What Our","titleHighlight":"Clients Say","readMore":"Learn More","readLess":"Read Less","items":[{"name":"Engineer Rami Abu Bakr","role":"Al Ramz Construction Projects Company | Kingdom of Saudi Arabia","content":"My sincere thanks and appreciation to Dr. Talat and the team accompanying the course. Frankly, it was a very special training course on a personal level. To be honest, the goal was not only to pass the exam and obtain the certificate, but rather my goal was to learn and apply project management in the real world, given our work as engineers and site managers."},{"name":"Dr. Faten Al-Buaishi Al-Kilani","role":"Lecturer at the Faculty of Law, University of Tripoli | Libya","content":"I enrolled in Dr. Talaat Alawady’s training program on professional project management, believing the scope of the information and skills I would receive would be beyond the scope of the program. I wondered what benefits I could gain from a specialty so far removed from this training program, as I had previously believed. I later discovered, while lecturing at law schools in Libyan universities, that I had acquired numerous significant skills that refined my approach to giving and presenting."},{"name":"Faisal Al-Shabahi","role":"Manager, Jeddah Municipality","content":"Many thanks to Trainer Talat Al-Awadi for this course (Professional Project Management). It played a significant role in broadening my understanding and knowledge of project management, addressing real-world scenarios with wisdom and effective management—an approach that yields numerous practical benefits. I also extend my gratitude to the team at the Dar Al-Ibdaa Center for their outstanding efforts, as well as to my fellow trainees; it was a pleasure working and collaborating with them throughout the course."}]},"contact":{"badge":"GET IN TOUCH","title":"Let's Build Something","titleHighlight":"Amazing","description":"Ready to transform your business? Reach out and let's discuss how we can help you achieve your goals.","emailLabel":"Email Us","phoneLabel":"Call Us","visitLabel":"Visit Us","emailValue":"info@creativity-house.com","phoneValue":"+60 3-1234 5678","visitValue":"Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia","form":{"name":"Full Name","namePlaceholder":"John Doe","email":"Email Address","emailPlaceholder":"john@company.com","subject":"Subject","subjectPlaceholder":"How can we help?","message":"Message","messagePlaceholder":"Tell us about your project...","send":"Send Message","sending":"Sending...","sent":"Message Sent!"}},"footer":{"description":"Empowering businesses with innovative IT solutions, custom software, and expert training since 2015.","servicesTitle":"Services","contactTitle":"Contact","serviceLinks":["CRM Systems","Project Management","Cloud Solutions","Training"],"legal":{"copyright":"© 2026 Creativity House Sdn Bhd. All rights reserved.","privacy":"Privacy Policy","terms":"Terms of Service"}},"languageSwitcher":{"label":"العربية"},"about_page":{"hero":{"badge":"Who We Are","title1":"Creativity House —","titleHighlight":"Building the Future of Organizations","description":"Creativity House Sdn. Bhd. is a multinational training, consulting, and technology solutions company specializing in administrative development, leadership empowerment, project management, and digital transformation. Founded in 2014 and headquartered in Cyberjaya, Malaysia since 2017, we have grown into a trusted partner for organizations across the Middle East, Africa, and Southeast Asia.","stats":[{"value":"10+","label":"Years of Experience"},{"value":"17+","label":"Countries Reached"},{"value":"3","label":"Regional Operations"}],"vision":{"title":"Our Vision","text":"To be the global first choice in administrative and leadership development, empowering individuals and organizations to achieve sustainable success and measurable impact."},"mission":{"title":"Our Mission","text":"To deliver innovative, practical, and technology-driven training and consulting services that develop human capabilities, strengthen institutional performance, and accelerate digital adoption in modern organizations."}},"social_proof":{"badge":"Trusted Worldwide","title":"Partnered with","titleHighlight":"World-Class Organizations","description":"From global energy companies to leading universities, our clients trust Creativity House to develop their people and transform their institutions.","testimonials":[{"name":"Dr. Faten Al-Buaishi Al-Kilani","role":"Lecturer, Faculty of Law — University of Tripoli, Libya","quote":"I acquired numerous and profound skills that significantly enhanced the way I deliver content. All thanks to Eng. Talaat Al-Awadhi."},{"name":"Eng. Rami Abu Bakr","role":"Al Ramz Construction Projects — Kingdom of Saudi Arabia","quote":"A lagging project was transformed into an architectural masterpiece. The criticism turned into sincere praise."},{"name":"Consultant Eng. Fathi Al-Jahdhami","role":"Engineering Consultant","quote":"I wholeheartedly recommend anyone seeking to understand project management to enroll in this comprehensive program."},{"name":"Mr. Faisal Al-Shabahi","role":"Manager, Jeddah Municipality","quote":"Played a significant role in expanding my knowledge and understanding of projects."},{"name":"Dr. Oussama Ouidane","role":"Senior Professional","quote":"The scientific content is worth its weight in gold. I am now a candidate for Executive Director."}]},"trainer":{"badge":"The Trainer","title":"Meet the","titleHighlight":"Expert Behind the Excellence","name":"Eng. Talaat Al-Awadhi","jobTitle":"International Trainer in Leadership, Management & Project Management","bio_label":"Biography","bio":"Engineer Talaat Hassan Al-Awadhi is a certified international trainer and expert in the fields of management, leadership, and skills development. He brings over 20 years of extensive experience delivering specialized training to public and private institutions across the Middle East, Africa, and Southeast Asia.","credentials_label":"Academic Credentials","credentials":["BSc Petroleum Engineering","Master of Business Administration (MBA)","PhD Candidate — Technology Management"],"expertise_label":"Areas of Expertise","expertise":["Project Management","Leadership & Coaching","Strategic Planning"],"badges":["20+ Years","Certified Trainer","International"]}}},"lang":"en"}]
